Intro Sometimes in EXWM when I switch machines to and plug in my dock to an already running system, one or two of my external monitors stay black1. Sometimes this also occurs when my smart-dock2 changes power levels to the dock. It has enough throughput to utilize my whole 100w power inlet, but its &ldquo;smarts&rdquo; mean that when I connect my USBC phone, for instance, the amount of power going out changes dramatically and the shift can &ldquo;lose&rdquo; my two HDMI monitors until I do the trick below.